Installation
------------
Here is how to build and install it::
  $ sudo apt-get install help2man gettext libxml2-dev automake bison build-essential flex libtool libclutter-1.0-dev
  $ ./autogen.sh
  $ ./configure
  $ make
  $ sudo make install

